.TH "dpni_set_offload" 9 "dpni_set_offload" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
dpni_set_offload \- Set DPNI offload configuration.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" dpni_set_offload
.BI "(struct fsl_mc_io *mc_io "  ","
.BI "u32 cmd_flags "  ","
.BI "u16 token "  ","
.BI "enum dpni_offload type "  ","
.BI "u32 config "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "mc_io" 12
Pointer to MC portal's I/O object
.IP "cmd_flags" 12
Command flags; one or more of 'MC_CMD_FLAG_'
.IP "token" 12
Token of DPNI object
.IP "type" 12
Type of DPNI offload
.IP "config" 12
Offload configuration.
For checksum offloads, non-zero value enables the offload
.SH "RETURN"
'0' on Success; Error code otherwise.
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
\fIwarning\fP    Allowed only when DPNI is disabled
